    UPS Tracking Number: <%= order.shipment.tracking %><br /><br />
    To track your package, go to:<br />
    <a href="http://wwwapps.ups.com/etracking/tracking.cgi?build_ttn=yes">UPS Tracking</a>
  <% end %>
</p>

